{
  "texts": [
    "GenAI refers broadly to any AI system that can produce new content.",
    "This can include generating text, images, music, or other types of content.",
    "LLMs are a specific type of GenAI that focuses on natural language processing.",
    "Following the media attention that ChatGPT received and the high number of users, higher education institutions (HEIs) displayed varied responses to the new AI systems.",
    "Among the top 500 universities listed in the 2022 Quacquarelli Symonds World University Rankings, the foremost 43 universities have implemented policies to ban ChatGPT, restricting the use of ChatGPT or any other AI tools during exams unless explicitly permitted (Xiao et al., 2023)."
  ]
}